<li>Hodges, Devon. "<i>Frankenstein</i> and the Feminine Subversion of the Novel". <i>Tulsa Studies in Women's Literature</i> 2.2 (1983): 155–64.</li>
<li>Hoeveler, Diane Long. <i>Gothic Feminism: The Professionalization of Gender from Charlotte Smith to the Brontës</i>. University Park: Pennsylvania State University Press, 1998.</li>
