<li>Rauch, Alan. "The Monstrous Body of Knowledge in Mary Shelley's <i>Frankenstein</i>". <i>Studies in Romanticism</i> 34.2 (1995): 227–53.</li>
<li>Selbanev, Xtopher. "Natural Philosophy of the Soul", Western Press, 1999.</li>
<li>Schor, Esther, ed. <i>The Cambridge Companion to Mary Shelley</i>. Cambridge: Cambridge University Press, 2003.</li>
